The paper discusses incremental view maintenance (IVM) for nested relational calculus (NRC+) on bags, which is a topic related to database management systems (cs.DB). The paper also involves the modeling of costs for NRC+ operators, which is a topic related to computational complexity theory (cs.CC) and logic in computer science (cs.LO). The paper proposes a translation from NRC+ to a fragment called IncNRC+, which is a topic related to programming languages (cs.PL). Finally, the paper discusses the application of recursive IVM, which is a topic related to data structures (cs.DS).
